<http://www.semanticweb.org/ayca/ontologies/2026/3/university-kg> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Extended ontology for Manisa Celal Bayar University Engineering Faculty. Models courses, academic staff, departments, and sub-fields. Version 2 adds MandatoryCourse/ElectiveCourse subclasses, ResearchAssistant class, SubField class, extended data properties, and real data from CSE, MEE, and IE departments."@en .
