<ukg:person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Person"@en .
# 
# ukg:professor
<ukg:professor> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<ukg:professor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <ukg:academicStaff> .
